title: Bug 49235 - ServletContainerInitializer onStartup classSet is not as expected
description: The output of ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) is "MySomeClass".
OB: The output of ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) is "MySomeClass".
EB: The output of ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) is not as expected, it should not be "MySomeClass".
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Invoke the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup method with a Set of Class objects (classSet) as input.
2. Check the output and observe that it is "MySomeClass" instead of the expected output.
